Package: safecleanr
Title: Simple and Safe Tools for Cleaning and Summarizing Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Sabin Ku", "Shah", , "shahs@lawrence.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides beginner-friendly tools for common data cleaning tasks.
    Functions include handling missing values via removal or imputation,
    safely joining two data frames with key validation, and generating
    quick summary statistics for numeric columns.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
